Package: samplingNR
Type: Package
Title: Stratified sample allocation under anticipated nonresponse
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: person("Jonathan", "Mendelson", email = "jmendelson@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5575-8773"))
Author: Jonathan Mendelson [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5575-8773>)
Maintainer: Jonathan Mendelson <jmendelson@gmail.com>
Description: Computes stratified sample allocations in a manner that accounts for anticipated nonresponse. Theory is provided in Mendelson & Elliott, "Optimal allocation under anticipated nonresponse," in press at the Journal of Survey Statistics and Methodology.
